8w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/12103713\/white-console-table-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Add decor pieces to accentuate the beauty of the console table<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Contemporary Console Table With Storage\u00a0<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>TV unit, statement furniture, and console table with storage all in one? That&#8217;s possible if you choose a design inspired by modern elements and contemporary colours. A beige top with a black rounded silhouette is narrow but spacious enough to hold anything you need to put away.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/12103633\/contemporary-console-table-with-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Contemporary console table with a beige top and a black rounded silhouette storage\" class=\"wp-image-51569\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/12103633\/contemporary-console-table-with-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/12103633\/contemporary-console-table-with-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/12103633\/contemporary-console-table-with-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/12103633\/contemporary-console-table-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Use the centre to place TV-related paraphernalia<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"End to end modular home interiors for indian homes\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/26111433\/End-